title: Norge Dishwasher Upper Spray Arm Nut
description: Norge Dishwasher Upper Spray Arm Nut ★★★★★ ★★★★★ 3 Reviews PartSelect Number PS11738161 Manufacturer Part Number W10877037 This upper spray arm nut is three inches long. It attaches to the spray arm to help hold it in place. It is all white in color and is made of plastic.

installationInstructions.author: Alane from Piedmont, OK
installationInstructions.title: spray arm would not stay on during wash
installationInstructions.content: Removed old spray arm and spray arm nut with a twist of my fingers.  Screwed in new spray nut with my hand, and snapped in the new spray arm.  Works PERFECTLY!  I did it all by myself! Saved me a costly plumber bill!  I am soooo proud of myself!
